    {
      "type": "plaintext",
      "content": "The main usage of this manager is for registering \"global loot modifiers\", also known as \"loot modifiers\" for\r\n short. A global loot modifier runs on the loot drop of every loot table (unless otherwise specified by conditions)\r\n and is as such able to modify it according either to predetermined parameters (e.g. replacing items) or via\r\n completely customized code that leverages the dropping context."
    },
    {
      "type": "new_line"
    },
    {
      "type": "new_line"
    },
